<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>sẖkrạaⁿ lrb fḍlh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- sẖkrạ lrb fḍlh bḥr ṭmạ zkẖạr
 yrwy ạltẖry̱ mn jwdh ạ̹dẖ yrsl ạlạ̉mṭạr

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: jmyʿ mạ nḥyạ bh mn fḍlh ạlʿmym
   flnsẖkrnh dạỷmạ lḥbh ạlʿẓym

[V2]
 2- yubdy lnạ mn sẖmshi ḥr̃ạ bh nḥyạ
 wmin nusaymạti ạlṣãbạ wgẖytẖhi nurwy̱

[V3]
 3- kl ạlwry̱ mn kẖlq mn qd ạ̉bdʿ ạlạ̉kwạn
 wzạn bạlnjm ạldjy̱ fạ̉bhj ạlạ̹nsạn

[V4]
 4- wạ̉ṭʿm ạlạ̉ṭyạr min ạ̉tẖmạr gẖrshi
 fkm lnạ yuʿṭy ạ̹dẖạ mn ʿrsẖ qdshi

[V5]
 5- nsẖkrk ạllhm mn ạ̉jl ʿṭạyạk
 fạlmạl wạlṣḥẗ wạlḥyạẗu jadwạk

[V6]
 6- fạqbl ạ̹dẖạ yạ rbnạ mn ạ̉jl dẖạ ạlạ̹ḥsạn
 mnạ qlwbạ mlw̉hạʿwạṭf ạlsẖkrạn</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1319</hymn_number>
<author>Jane M. Campbell</author>
</song>